## Data Loading

```python
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np

# Load your data
df_train = pd.read_csv('../data/X_train.csv')
df_test = pd.read_csv('../data/X_test.csv')
y_train = np.load('../data/y_train.npy')
y_test = np.load('../data/y_test.npy')
```

